evidence.source_document: Notice of Appeal of Final Judgment of Plaintiff Andrew H. Warren
evidence.text: Plaintiff Andrew H. Warren hereby appeals to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit from the Final Order (ECF No. 150) and Judgment (ECF No. 151) of the United States District Court for the Northern District of Florida entered on January 20, 2023, the Honorable Robert L. Hinkle presiding.

extracted.value: Appeal: Andrew H. Warren appealed to United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit.
